                            <comment id="14085993" author="irisding" created="Tue, 5 Aug 2014 08:25:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The fix  is simply to catch the ClassCastException and return it as an InternalServerErrorException:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;catch (ClassCastException e) &lt;/p&gt;
{ 
            String msg = &quot;Unsupported class: &quot; + source.getName();
            throw ExceptionUtils.toInternalServerErrorException(null, serverError(msg));
 }

&lt;p&gt;The proposed patch will be attached .&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Iris Ding&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14086104" author="sergey_beryozkin" created="Tue, 5 Aug 2014 10:47:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for a patch, the only minor update I did was to do with logging an error message rather than reporting back to the client the signature details&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
